message: Let's split it 50/50, a fair start!
I'll take 60, you get 40, a good starting point!
Meet me in the middle, I'll give you 55
You're getting low, I'll take 70, you get 30, it's my turn now!
Meet me at 42, it's getting serious!
You're running out of time, I'll take 80, you get 20, it's my last chance!
Last chance, I'll give you 60, don't leave me with nothing!
